{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":12,"day":25}],"page_start":4,"page_end":4,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"卜算子","authors":["叶剑英"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"社教入农村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万众欢如许。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落落千年血泪仇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作银锄舞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"努力造丰登，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓角催人去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战友天涯若比邻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合唱同袍赋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注释"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）如许：如此的意思。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）银锄舞：挥舞闪闪发亮的锄头。“化作银锄舞”，意思是说，劳动人民把千年血泪仇化为巨大的力量，发挥冲天干劲，大办农业。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）鼓角：战鼓、号角。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四）同袍：“袍”，军衣。古时军人互相称呼叫“同袍”。这里“同袍”指共同战斗。“合唱”的“合”字，解作应该。"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"叶剑英","type":"人物"},{"name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}